
Template: qdb-server/security
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Enable security?
 QuasarDB has a built-in authentication mechanism based on asymetric
 cryptography. This provides built-in support for full traffic encryption
 as well as message integrity. Traffic encryption requires authentication
 to be turned on.
 .
 If this is a production install, we recommend to enable security. If
 you are installing QuasarDB for evaluation and/or development purposes,
 we recommend to disable it.
